title: 02/01/22 DPS Hour 3 Sam Webb and Bill Plaschke

description:
Sam Webb tells Dan that if the Vikings offer Jim Harbaugh the head coaching position, Harbaugh will take it. Sam says the window for Harbaugh is now. Bill Plaschke says that Matthew Stafford and the Rams must win because Jared Goff got the Rams to a Super Bowl too.
